com.helger.jcodemodel

Interface IJAssignmentTarget

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IJExpression, IJGenerable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractJExpressionAssignmentTargetImpl, JArrayCompRef, JFieldRef, JFieldVar, JLambdaParam, JVar

    public interface IJAssignmentTarget
extends IJExpression
    Marker interface for code components that can be placed to the left of '=' in an assignment. A left hand value can always be a right hand value, so this interface derives from IJExpression.
